summary.description: Mulamuleli is a Bachelor of Sciences in Physical Sciences graduate with a keen interest in developing her mathematical reasoning, deductive reasoning, information-ordering, and Decision-Making skills. As a highly energetic and team-orientated individual, I am eager to apply skills in a professional environment and contribute to the success of the team

experience.Charity-Work: I worked under the Mr Majo Foundation, a non-profit organization, we volunteered to prepare food and tea for the elderly in 2018 while they camped out in front of the bank every day to be able to withdraw cash during the VBS bank collapse tragedy. After that, we went on to gather used clothing that is in good condition and gave it to others in need.
